        <Summary>Cross-platform, 3D and historically-based real-time strategy game of ancient warfare</Summary>
        <Description>0 A.D. is a free, open-source, cross-platform real-time strategy (RTS) game of ancient warfare. In short, it is a historically-based war/economy game that allows players to relive or rewrite the history of Western civilizations, focusing on the years between 500 B.C. and 500 A.D.</Description>
